      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GRANT KEEPING (1) was quickly out of the tricky draw with a fast early sectional and clocked 29.63 with a 5.5 lengths win at this track over 520m. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from three attempts. Looks the testing material. BOOM BAM RANGER (2) found the frame for the second consecutive time when narrowly beaten into third last time out (25.66) over 457m at Q Lakeside. Can improve sharply here. EXEQUIEL (3) looks close to win after hitting the frame last run (30.00) at this track in a Restricted WIN. Has first look at box 3 this time. Expected to be in this for a long way. BEFORE THE DAWN (8) warrants respect although new to this track.",
